00:05:07.530 --> 00:05:13.830
They just, in my life, I believe
through my parents who are born

00:05:13.830 --> 00:05:17.770
in the early 20th century,
1908 and 1916.

00:05:17.770 --> 00:05:22.520
They were of the generation of
the association for the study

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:25.570
of Negro life and history.

00:05:25.570 --> 00:05:30.120
Founded by Carter G. Woodson,
it was very meticulous

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:33.340
and scrupulous groundbreaking
