black scholars and blacks wanting

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:46.910 position:56%
to be educated really knew about it.

00:05:46.910 --> 00:05:51.230
It mirrored in that way
a segregated nation.

00:05:51.230 --> 00:05:57.270
When I came along in the-- I
was born at the end of '40s.

00:05:57.270 --> 00:06:01.280
