00:11:59.780 --> 00:12:01.580
for a writer can't come out.

00:12:01.580 --> 00:12:05.510
So I started to feel acutely
uncomfortable and I would get angry

00:12:05.510 --> 00:12:11.550
and jealous when other writers
were turning out memoirs or novels

00:12:11.550 --> 00:12:14.390
that I thought they're
expressing something.

00:12:14.390 --> 00:12:20.310
I'm not. And then frankly, in
2008, I got a grant for it.

00:12:20.310 --> 00:12:23.180
And then my sister who was
three years older than I

00:12:23.180 --> 00:12:25.560
and the director of
