00:13:32.220 --> 00:13:37.180
very detailed, and
also very painful.

00:13:37.180 --> 00:13:41.030
And I wondered if you could
talk a little bit about that

00:13:41.030 --> 00:13:43.380
and how you feel about it now?

00:13:43.380 --> 00:13:49.220 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: Well, you know,
