00:13:49.220 --> 00:13:54.100
so called elite of an--

00:13:54.100 --> 00:14:00.200
discriminated against to
oppressed group is very peculiar.

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:04.450
You certainly-- you're
a fool and you're a liar

00:14:04.450 --> 00:14:07.970
