that you are sheltered

00:14:07.970 --> 00:14:11.620
and privileged in many ways.

00:14:11.620 --> 00:14:14.940
Where I think the pain
and the-- came is--

00:14:14.940 --> 00:14:23.290
you know, it's partly the old W.
E. B. Du Bois double consciousness.

00:14:23.290 --> 00:14:28.400
We were constantly living
out and living up to all

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:32.960
of the accomplishments
and achievements

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:35.240
of black people, of Negroes.

00:14:35.240 --> 00:14:38.780
And that's where we did know
or were taught black history.

00:14:38.780 --> 00:14:44.020
At the same time we knew perfectly
well that if we did not proved

00:14:44.020 --> 00:14:46.470
in terms of manners,
our accomplishments,

00:14:46.470 --> 00:14:51.700
