00:14:58.640 --> 00:15:00.820
That leads both

00:15:00.820 --> 00:15:05.740
to self consciousness a
struggle with self hatred.

00:15:05.740 --> 00:15:07.040
&gt;&gt; Marcia Davis: Yeah.

00:15:07.040 --> 00:15:08.340
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: And
that was very difficult.

00:15:08.340 --> 00:15:14.350 position:56%
Also there was kind of self scrutiny
particularly for girls, I would say.

00:15:14.350 --> 00:15:18.170
You know, this constant
surveillance and watching

00:15:18.170 --> 00:15:21.040
