00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:22.360
Am I a lady?

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:26.030
We were-- As girls
were busy combating.

00:15:26.030 --> 00:15:30.080
We had been taught the history
of a black women which included--

00:15:30.080 --> 00:15:32.560
