00:32:44.350 --> 00:32:45.650
&gt;&gt; Marcia Davis: OK.

00:32:45.650 --> 00:32:49.090
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: But she's
still have a joie de vivre,

00:32:49.090 --> 00:32:51.530
