00:32:51.530 --> 00:32:57.250 position:56%
I feel-- This is-- No, I don't know.

00:32:57.250 --> 00:32:59.880
She also had a much
more deliberately.

00:32:59.880 --> 00:33:06.590
She lived the life of an
intelligent upper middle class wife

00:33:06.590 --> 00:33:09.090
in the '40s, '50s, and '60s.

00:33:09.090 --> 00:33:14.630
And that meant a certain
kind of security albeit

00:33:14.630 --> 00:33:16.710
with difficulties as
we feminist know.

00:33:16.710 --> 00:33:19.860
That was a life that
you could structure

00:33:19.860 --> 00:33:22.220
in certain ways to be pretty safe.

00:33:22.220 --> 00:33:25.160
And if you are very
resourceful about it

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:28.190 position:56%
