00:33:28.190 --> 00:33:36.910
My generation, and thank God,
we were shaped by civil rights,

00:33:36.910 --> 00:33:41.010
black power, antiwar,
feminism, women's movement,

00:33:41.010 --> 00:33:43.620
gay rights, you know, boom.

00:33:43.620 --> 00:33:44.920
&gt;&gt; Marcia Davis: Right.

00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:46.910
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: But the
excitement and the pleasure,

00:33:46.910 --> 00:33:50.800
the story of life, you know, the
sense of freedom was supposed

00:33:50.800 --> 00:33:58.810
