00:34:09.520 --> 00:34:12.140
It's also a-- you know,
it's also kind of thrilling.

00:34:12.140 --> 00:34:14.690
It's pretty thrilling
and it was essential.

00:34:14.690 --> 00:34:16.700
It was just utterly necessary.

00:34:16.700 --> 00:34:19.590
So we're looking for different
