00:37:16.190 --> 00:37:18.130
all of their friends were black.

00:37:18.130 --> 00:37:19.910
My father was pediatrician.

00:37:19.910 --> 00:37:21.840
He had patients from all classes.

00:37:21.840 --> 00:37:29.330 position:56%
But I can't pretend that-- I won't
pretend that we made lots of friends

00:37:29.330 --> 00:37:31.100
across those class lines.

00:37:31.100 --> 00:37:32.400
We did not.

00:37:32.400 --> 00:37:36.540
But we did live in an
all black neighborhood.

00:37:36.540 --> 00:37:41.570
And, you know, I was
most familiar in terms

00:37:41.570 --> 00:37:45.150 position:56%
of that day-to-day life with blacks.

00:37:45.150 --> 00:37:48.540
But no, those class lines
