00:38:01.160 --> 00:38:03.370
We love imitating it.

00:38:03.370 --> 00:38:06.570
But, yeah, we were playing
exotic a little bit.

00:38:06.570 --> 00:38:10.180
That's what class distinctions do.

00:38:10.180 --> 00:38:11.480
