00:39:27.580 --> 00:39:28.880
&gt;&gt; And I guess my question was--

00:39:28.880 --> 00:39:30.710
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson:
And it was excruciating

00:39:30.710 --> 00:39:34.140
