00:40:41.400 --> 00:40:44.490
So you-- yeah.

00:40:44.490 --> 00:40:49.540
Yeah, you veer between
bearing it and using it.

00:40:51.170 --> 00:40:54.180
&gt;&gt; Marcia Davis: Sir with
