00:40:57.010 --> 00:40:59.040
I like it a lot.

00:40:59.040 --> 00:41:02.980 position:56%
I can see that the black
experience which I have not had is--

00:41:02.980 --> 00:41:04.280
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: I'm sorry.

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:05.810
