&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: Absolutely.

00:43:38.780 --> 00:43:40.080
&gt;&gt; -- oftentimes.

00:43:40.080 --> 00:43:41.720
And I'm just wondering in looking
at that consumptious [phonetic],

00:43:41.720 --> 00:43:45.180
that conspicuous consumption
looking at it,

00:43:45.180 --> 00:43:50.680
do you see the Negroland shifting
in 2016, these Negrolands,

00:43:50.680 --> 00:43:54.140
are those spaces having to
adapt and to adjust to the way

00:43:54.140 --> 00:43:58.160
in which the cultural
landscape is moving

00:43:58.160 --> 00:44:00.250
and those new tensions
that are being created?

00:44:00.250 --> 00:44:01.550
&gt;&gt; Margo Jefferson: Absolutely.

00:44:01.550 --> 00:44:04.090
First of all, it's been
having to adjust just

00:44:04.090 --> 00:44:07.740
